## Project Structure

```
src/{{langConfig.moduleName}}/
  client.py          # Main client class
  _http_client.py    # HTTP layer with retry logic (httpx)
  _auth.py           # OAuth 2.0 implementation
  _pagination.py     # Async pagination iterator
  _errors.py         # Error class hierarchy
  resources/         # One file per API resource
tests/               # Unit tests (pytest)
  integration/       # Integration tests
docs/                # API documentation per resource
```

## Key Patterns

- All methods are async (`async def`) and must be awaited
- Uses httpx for async HTTP
- Pydantic v2 models for request/response types
- snake_case naming throughout
- Path parameters are passed as keyword arguments
- Query parameters (filters, pagination) are passed as optional keyword arguments

